# sort-after-sort

## Description

Migrated from the hand-coded `functional_dependency_rules` to a declarative `.rra` rule
(RFC 0090). The rewrite is expressed as structured data below.

## Rewrite

lhs: (sort ?keys1 (sort ?keys2 ?input))
rhs: (sort ?keys1 ?input)
